headline: Beck Bode Initiates Churchill Downs Position as Regional Gaming Expansion Lifts Growth Prospects
summary: Churchill Downs isn’t just about one race weekend a year. The company is expanding casinos and historical racing venues designed to produce recurring gaming revenue, and investors are weighing whether that investment phase will pay off.
